image_analysis.description: A financial disclosure form, specifically OGE Form 278e, detailing the ownership structure of various business entities associated with Donald J. Trump. The page is numbered A36 of 47.
image_analysis.layout: The document is structured as a form with distinct sections for each business entity, identified by a reference number. Each section lists the entity name, ownership percentages, and the names and roles of the owners. A header contains form information and the filer's name, and a footer contains a document identifier.
